&lt;p&gt;Schonfeld&#39;s Enterprise Data team is looking for a Market Data Analyst to manage the sourcing, licensing, and entitlements of market data across global vendors, exchanges, and brokers. You&#39;ll support Schonfeld’s quantitative, fundamental, tactical, and macro portfolio managers in managing access to datasets across multiple asset classes and regions.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;What You’ll Do&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Oversee day to day user entitlements, usage tracking, and compliance with vendor agreements and exchange rules&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage vendor relationships (Bloomberg, LSEG, etc.), including licensing, onboarding, and cost optimization&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help manage exchange audits and compliance queries, ensuring accurate usage reporting and timely resolution with vendors and internal stakeholders&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain inventory accuracy within the Optimize Spend platform while driving cost transparency and consolidation opportunities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor data usage, troubleshoot discrepancies, and enforce data integrity controls&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain documentation of data sources, workflows, and governance processes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;What You’ll Bring&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor’s degree in finance, Accounting, or Business&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;2–5 years in market data, data operations, or a related role at a hedge fund, asset manager, or financial services firm&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong analytical and problem-solving skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deep understanding of financial data, data vendors, and their licensing structures.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Hands-on experience with Bloomberg EMRS, Refinitiv DACS, and Optimize Spend&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;SQL and/or scripting experience is a plus&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Enthusiasm for leveraging AI tools to improve productivity and decision-making&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
