&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking a highly qualified and talented technologist to join us as a member of our Network Engineering team. The team is responsible for the architecture, design, administration and support of our global network infrastructure.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you’ll do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;The Network Engineer will help support and expand the networking environment at Schonfeld. You will research&amp;nbsp;requirements and interact with multiple internal and external stakeholders to implement and deploy our global network&amp;nbsp;infrastructure. You will participate in the implementation, operations and troubleshooting of our global network&amp;nbsp;infrastructure. The ideal candidate has the ability to consistently apply broad knowledge of network administration to the&amp;nbsp;diagnosis and resolution of network problems.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you’ll bring&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;What you need:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;At minimum, 3 years of experience in a network engineering role focusing on enterprise network design and administration&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with routing and switching in a Cisco/Arista environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with Next Gen Firewalls - Palo Alto, Fortinet&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with WiFi technologies - Meraki&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Detailed knowledge of BGP, and OSPF network routing protocols&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with Multicast routing concepts including the use of PIM, and IGMP&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with common network management protocols such as SNMP, TACACS, Netflow, Sflow&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience supporting Linux infrastructure&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We’d love if you had:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Automation Mindset&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Python&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ansible&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Network overlay concepts - VXLAN and eVPN&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with cloud - AWS and Azure&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with network disaster recovery&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Financial Services experience a plus&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;Our Culture&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
