&lt;p&gt;- Design, develop, and maintain high-performance applications, including market data, order management systems, and trading systems.&lt;br&gt;- Optimize and enhance existing software to improve performance and scalability.&lt;br&gt;- Ensure the reliability and robustness of trading systems through rigorous testing and live monitoring.&lt;br&gt;- Participate in code reviews and contribute to best practices in software development.&lt;br&gt;- Stay up-to-date with the latest technologies and industry trends to drive innovation.&lt;/p&gt;
