&lt;li&gt;Build, deploy, and maintain internal tools and dashboards that surface quantitative outputs, portfolio analytics, and market data in clean, intuitive interfaces, actively used by investment professionals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to the AI integration layer in close coordination with central Technology teams: strategically implementing and operating AI capabilities tailored to the specific needs of the Fundamental Equity business, spanning LLM APIs, MCP servers, and agentic workflows, with the awareness that this is a rapidly evolving landscape requiring continuous reassessment of what best looks like&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work closely with quant researchers to take analytical outputs from prototype to reliable, production-ready applications&lt;/li&gt;
